{"tid":148594,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【祝早日康復！】專科醫生Stand by 82歲譚炳文氣喘送院面容消瘦","createTime":"2017-03-08T16:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T08:40:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d29a0e88005c710c17d3003bc5012cb433a5fa44","tid":148594,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"演而優則配音嘅資料男藝員譚炳文，近日少咗喺幕前演出，但佢把聲仲不時會聽到，包括喺廣告同節目旁白等，一直冇停過工，不過，據其親友噚晚約10點幾喺社交網站貼相透露，原來炳哥因氣喘入咗醫院！<br />\n<br />\n據知，呢幾日炳哥都見唔舒服，氣喘咗兩、三日，佢個妹得知後，適逢有相熟嘅胸肺專科及心臟專科喺醫院，所以嗱嗱聲送咗炳哥入去檢查，一check就發現唔嘢少，所以炳哥啲親友都話好彩，發現及時。<br />\n睇番啲相，見到炳哥雖然要戴氧氣罩，但精神都OK，不過就比佢今年1月出席盆菜宴時，明顯瘦咗一個圈，話晒炳哥都大年紀，的確係幾令人擔心嘅。<br />\n小編謹祝炳哥早日康復出院，多多保重身體。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170308/large/1488988345_ad51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170308%2Flarge%2F1488988345_ad51.jpg&h=59687bc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0eb163f1cee5cbefe907b769362f4dd70f923b60","tid":148594,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adb4a3978e0c937d778564d8d4146e2f5c37810","tid":148594,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acc9e90a5ea31f000a153e691f2400822dd78b7","tid":148594,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc55d6844192255e82cf7b6be8ad514f18020ae","tid":148594,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be15c889870c370043e41583e8